ca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 11, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56667\">STS Test Results</a> by Michael B, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 14, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67728\">LcZero and STS</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 14, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Strategic_Test_Suite&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/strategictestsuite/\">Strategic Test Suite</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rebel13.nl/rebel13/pet.html\">Practical Engine Tuning</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, June 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a> using STS</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/fsmosca/STS-Rating\">GitHub - fsmosca/STS-Rating: A method to rate chess engines using STS test suite</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\